{"tid":1565082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日買蘋果日報 送光榮香港小黃燈","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:26:18.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"724941a6ae2d5ca822d1ad2895ccd633f21196fa","tid":1565082,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》於今日（13日）隨報附送「光復香港小黃燈」，應節之餘亦讓讀者毋忘「光復香港，時代革命」、「五大訴求，缺一不可」，《蘋果》亦會與大家一起「齊上齊落」。<br />\n<br />\n讀者們只需剪下紙樣，沿紙樣的線條作簡單摺合再黏貼，小黃燈便大功告成（步驟見下圖）。摺好小黃燈後，大家可亮起手機電筒，再將小黃燈放上，將一點點黃光，織成一條又一條小黃燈之路。這個中秋，港人抗爭之路並不孤單。<br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果日報》今日隨報附送「光復香港」小黃燈】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Qo11Wj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Qo11Wj&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=14f755e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Qo11Wj</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🚨今日新疆 明日香港<br />\n《囚牢之疆》專頁揭集中營邪惡面紗：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PGSSf8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PGSSf8&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=377fa29e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2PGSSf8</a><br />\n==============<br />\n📣 召集有心人！半價贊助學生全年睇蘋果<br />\n我要撐學生 / 我是學生：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PvsUuK&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=d9ad5fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2PvsUuK</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 新聞有價，用真相對抗不義<br />\n訂閱撐蘋果，每日只需HK$1.68：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KFbs1f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KFbs1f&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=7f78bf51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2KFbs1f</a>"},{"pid":"3f3ee429e74a65d6eeec87e18b50d94f960865fb","tid":1565082,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/face